# Homelab Rules

## Intent
Document the homelab as an enterprise lab: segmented, monitored, recoverable, and evidence-backed.

## Conventions
- Link hosts to [[Homelab Inventory]].
- Map capabilities to [[Homelab Maturity Model]].
- Every lab scenario belongs in [[Lab Catalog]] or a child note.
- Prefer system notes from Homelab System Template.

## Naming
- VMs/LXCs: `role-name-##`
- Keep zone labels consistent with networking docs.

## Required Links
- [[ARCHITECTURE]]
- [[Networking Overview]]
- [[Infrastructure Overview]]
